<mjml>
  <mj-include path="./head.mjml" />
  <mj-body mj-class="body">
    <mj-wrapper background-color="#F0F0F0">
      <mj-section />
      <mj-section css-class="section">
        <mj-column>
          <mj-text mj-class="headline"
            >Thanks for signing up to ReDI Connect!</mj-text
          >
          <mj-divider mj-class="divider-top" css-class="divider" />

          <mj-text mj-class="text" padding="0 0 20px 0"
            >Hi ${firstName},</mj-text
          >
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph" 
            >Thank you for signing up as a <strong>mentee</strong> on ReDI
            Connect!</mj-text
          >
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph" 
            >Your next step is to watch a short
            <strong>onboarding tutorial</strong> to get a good overview of the
            mentorship program and how our matching platform ReDI Connect
            works. You will use the platform to find your mentor and connect with them
            there.</mj-text
          >
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph">
            Please make sure to <strong>fully watch</strong> the onboarding
            tutorial because it contains all the
            <strong>information</strong> you need to be able to successfully
            navigate the platform and get a good understanding of what
            mentorship means in the ReDI context.
          </mj-text>
          <mj-image
            src="https://redi-connect-email-assets.s3.eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/redi-connect-sign-up-video-thumbnail.jpeg"
            align="left"
            padding="10px 0 30px 0"
            target="_blank"
            css-class="button-desktop"
            href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M3nwS3QfdMM"
          />
          <mj-image
            src="https://redi-connect-email-assets.s3.eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/redi-connect-sign-up-video-thumbnail.jpeg"
            align="left"
            padding="10px 0 30px 0"
            target="_blank"
            css-class="button-mobile"
            href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M3nwS3QfdMM"
          />
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph" 
            >Your <strong>final step</strong> after watching this video will be
            your <strong>activation call</strong> with our Mentorship Community
            Manager, <strong>Hadeer</strong>, who will be happy to answer any remaining questions
            and then activate your account - only then will you be able to
            fully use the platform and search for a mentor.</mj-text
          >
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph" 
            ><strong>Schedule your activation call now</strong> and make sure to
            watch the onboarding tutorial <strong>before</strong> attending your
            activation call - there won’t be time to explain everything from
            scratch during this call.</mj-text
          >
          <mj-image
            src="https://redi-connect-email-assets.s3.eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/schedule-activation-call-now-button.png"
            align="center"
            padding="10px 0 30px 0"
            target="_blank"
            width="358px"
            css-class="button-desktop"
            href="https://calendly.com/hadeertalentsucess/redi-connect-mentees-activation-call"
          />
          <mj-image
            src="https://redi-connect-email-assets.s3.eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/schedule-activation-call-now-button.png"
            align="left"
            padding="10px 0 30px 0"
            target="_blank"
            css-class="button-mobile"
            href="https://calendly.com/hadeertalentsucess/redi-connect-mentees-activation-call"
          />
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph" 
            >In case of any questions, you can
            <strong>message Hadeer on Slack</strong> or send us an
            <strong>e-mail</strong> at
            <strong>career@redischool.org</strong>.</mj-text
          >
          <mj-text mj-class="text paragraph" 
            >We’re looking forward to getting to know you soon!
          </mj-text>

          <mj-text mj-class="text">All the best,</mj-text>
          <mj-text mj-class="text">Your ReDI Career Support Team</mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-include path="./footer.career.support.team.mjml" />
      <mj-section />
    </mj-wrapper>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
